</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">H<span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">sub</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>2<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">sub</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>O
爆米<span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">sup</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>TM<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">sup</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>效果如下</p>
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O</p>
<p>爆米<sup>TM</sup></p>
<h3 id="字体颜色与字号">字体颜色与字号</h3>
<p>写法如下</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
