</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">table</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">tr</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
